3
00:00:17,590 --> 00:00:21,570
Before the age of nine, there are two stages that children progress through.

4
00:00:21,570 --> 00:00:25,520
Bearing in mind, Kohlberg wasn’t asking infants about morality – these kinds of

5
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:29,310
questions are really for children at the upper end of this age range.

6
00:00:29,310 --> 00:00:33,220
In the first stage, children would tend to argue that Joe should give the money to his

7
