25
00:01:39,479 --> 00:01:43,979
And, keep in mind that in Kohlberg levels, the ages he gives are approximate.

26
00:01:43,979 --> 00:01:47,869
There&#39;s no exact age where kids should or should not pass, but they should go through

27
00:01:47,869 --> 00:01:50,520
each of these levels in order.

28
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:55,820
At some point in time, around adolescence, children enter Stage 3, which is the first

29
00:01:55,820 --> 00:01:57,509
