32
00:02:06,490 --> 00:02:10,340
At this point, children are beginning to take a social, interpersonal perspective on these

33
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:11,340
dilemmas.

34
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:15,750
They are considering Joe&#39;s relationship with his father and how they&#39;re interacting, and

35
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:18,970
